OL,3,CNurses take trust to tribunal over
OL,4,Ctrans colleague's use of changing rooms
OL,6,FA group of nurses who are challenging
OL,7,Ftheir health trust's policy over
OL,8,Fallowing a trans colleague to use the
OL,9,Ffemale changing rooms at work have
OL,10,Fattended an employment tribunal
OL,11,Fhearing.
OL,13,FThe eight nurses are taking action
OL,14,Fagainst County Durham and Darlington
OL,15,FNHS Foundation Trust after a colleague
OL,16,Fwho was born male, but now identifies
OL,17,Fas a woman, was allowed to use the
OL,18,Fwomen's changing facilities at
OL,19,FDarlington Memorial Hospital.
