OL,3,CNurses take trust to tribunal over
OL,4,Ctrans colleague's use of changing rooms
OL,6,FThey have filed the claim on the
OL,7,Fgrounds of sexual harassment,
OL,8,Fdiscrimination, victimisation and
OL,9,Fbreaches of the right to a private
OL,10,Flife, under Article 8 of the European
OL,11,FConvention on Human Rights.
OL,13,FSeven of the nurses were at a
OL,14,Fpreliminary hearing at Newcastle
OL,15,FTribunal Centre where a judge
OL,16,Fdiscussed an application by the trust
OL,17,Fto delay the hearing from its current
OL,18,Ftrial date of 16 June.
